{
  "id": "4-2",
  "title": "Act 2: Crisis",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch4_act2_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "vignette",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Combat augmentation modules mounted on shoulders and forearms, neural interface cables embedded in the neck.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> Neural interface connection established",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The moment the connection established, {{characters.soren.name}} experienced something he had never felt before—as if the boundaries of his perception were forcibly stretched outward.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The heavy metal cannon attached to his arm's end suddenly became as tangible as his own fingers, every subtle movement directly perceptible.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "Flanking support. {{characters.soren.name}}, suppress the two o'clock, no need for a direct hit—just keep them at distance.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 28
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}} didn't hesitate. He aimed the module's cannon in the direction she indicated and fired.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 300,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 5
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The shockwave pushed both soldiers back a step. No effective damage, but the objective was achieved.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}}, rear left.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 28
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She was already closing in with the frontmost soldier in close range combat. Her frame was Beta maturity, with superior reaction time and strength compared to the three Alpha-frame children, but the soldier's military-grade shell meant each exchange was about trading speed and angle for space, not direct force.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}}, find cover. Don't expose yourself in open ground.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 28
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "Got it!",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She was already behind the storage racks, hugging the medical supplies tightly.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The problems began to manifest over time.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}} felt it. It wasn't physical fatigue, but something deeper—like something was being drawn out of his consciousness. At first a trickle, then increasingly faster.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The cannon's aim began to drift. He tried to correct it, but the effort itself brought another surge of depletion.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> Warning: Neural synchronization rate declining",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "He realized the root cause—his synchronization level was insufficient to sustain this heavy module. Forcing higher output was only accelerating the cycle.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}}, reduce output. Pull it down to what you can stabilize, just maintain.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "He complied. The cannon's drift stabilized, suppression effectiveness dropped, but at least the direction was reliable.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}}'s situation was worse.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "His instinct was hacking, not direct combat. Forcing control of a heavy module resulted in synchronization depletion far faster than {{characters.soren.name}} experienced. His right arm was already beginning to show slight, uncontrollable tremors—an early warning of neural connection overload.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "shake",
          "ms": 500,
          "args": {
            "intensity": 9
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "A soldier exploited the moment when his cannon aim drifted, charging directly through his defense.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}} couldn't dodge in time. He was rammed backwards, his back slamming hard against the storage racks as items clattered down around him.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "text": ">> Warning: Frame integrity compromised — Neural synchronization rate plummeting",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "He slid onto the floor, gritted his teeth, and pushed himself back up.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}}—can you access the signal network?",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "Give me a moment.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "Hold on.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} found a passage connecting the storage racks to the side wall from her sheltered position. She crawled through and flanked one of the soldiers approaching {{characters.soren.name}}.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She engaged her module at minimal output. Rather than trying to knock it down, she targeted its rear joint articulations with rapid, short-range electromagnetic pulses, causing its gait to momentarily destabilize.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "No decisive damage, but it gave {{characters.soren.name}} the opening to reposition.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}}'s frame was the smallest, with the lowest overload threshold. She kept her output minimal, doing one thing—keeping the enemy's attention distributed instead of focused on one target.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The fighting in the hall continued at a slow, exhausting pace.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 800,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "vignette",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "complete"
  ]
}
